msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid "Apprentice"
msgstr "弟子"

msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid "Apprentice"
msgstr "弟子"

msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You were an aspiring student of a well-learned master of the mysterious "
"arts.  Sadly, you had only just begun your apprenticeship when your master "
"was claimed by the end of the world."
msgstr ""
"師匠から神秘的な技術を操る方法を意欲的に学んでいました。師匠が世界の終焉に飲"
"み込まれてしまったので、残念ながらこれからは自力で学ぶしかありません。"

